  "biography_html": "<div class=\"research-section\">\n<p class=\"research-text\">Gorgon the Historian was active in the 4th–3rd centuries BCE. No details of his life, including his origins or education, are recorded. He is credited with a single prose work in Koine Greek, but its title, subject, and current status are unknown. Gorgon remains an obscure figure with no documented influence on the subsequent historiographical tradition.</p>\n</div>",
